OL,3,CCosmetics company fined #56,000 over
OL,4,Celectrocution risk
OL,6,FA cosmetics company in Halifax has
OL,7,Fbeen fined more than #50,000 after
OL,8,Finspectors found workers were at risk
OL,9,Fof being electrocuted.
OL,11,FThe Health and Safety Executive (HSE)
OL,12,Funcovered serious failings during
OL,13,Funannounced checks at Sabel Cosmetic
OL,14,FLimited's premises on Pellon Lane.
OL,16,FIt said electrical faults posed a
OL,17,Fserious risk of electric shock and
OL,18,Felectrocution to workers.
OL,20,FThe company had failed to address the
OL,21,Fproblems, inspectors said.
