OL,4,Celectrocution risk
OL,6,FSabel was fined #56,695 and ordered to
OL,7,Fpay legal costs after admitting health
OL,8,Fand safety breaches at Leeds
OL,9,FMagistrates Court.
OL,11,FHSE inspector Andrea Jones, said:
OL,12,F"This case shows the importance of HSE
OL,13,Finspections to help ensure health and
OL,14,Fsafety risks are being managed
OL,15,Feffectively and protect people at work.
OL,17,F"It is essential that electrical
OL,18,Fwiring installations and electrical
OL,19,Fequipment are constructed and
OL,20,Fmaintained in a safe condition to
OL,21,Fprevent injuries or even worse, death.
